fields.description:
For instance migration, if destination host is set to the source node, CLC returns a error message with not enough resources,

{noformat}
[root@h-05 ~]# euca-migrate-instances -i i-FD64408D --dest 10.111.5.33
Error(MigrateInstancesType): Migrating instance i-FD64408D failed because of: not enough resources available for migration
{noformat}

comments.body:
Also, migrate to another cluster gives the same output,

{noformat}
[root@c-19 ~]# euca-migrate-instances -i i-52044084 --dest 10.111.1.69
Error(MigrateInstancesType): Migrating instance i-52044084 failed because of: not enough resources available for migration
{noformat}
